Subject: AridZona VW Show

November 12, 2005 - Volkswagens by the River 4
Yuma, Arizona
Volkswagens by the River 4.
Saturday, November 12th, 8am to 2:30pm at the Colorado River Beach Park.
Located at 1st Street and Madison Avenue, in Yuma, Arizona.

Vehicle entry $5
Swap/Vendor spots $10
Spectator entry $1 or a can of food (donations to the Yuma Community Food
Bank)
Awards / Raffles / Kids events / T-shirts / Food
Raffle tickets are .50 cents each.

The day before is Veterans Day. Use the three day Holiday weekend to drive
out and spend the night with us at our campout, attend the show, and still
have a day and a half to get home. The desert is absolutely cool and
beautiful in November. Look at our listing for November 11, 2005 for more
details on the campout.

Approximate mileage to Yuma: Phoenix 180mi, Tucson 235mi, Lake Havasu 160mi,
Mexicali 60mi, San Diego 165mi, L.A. 230mi.

Information contacts:
Jim --- vwbum(-at-)adelphia.net
Steve --- vwfreak62(-at-)hotmail.com
Andrew --- wickedwater(-at-)msn.com

This show is back by popular request and is sponsored by:
VW enthusiasts of Yuma, Import Auto Supply of Yuma and the Arizona Bus Club.
